channel.title: [Delta] How do you remove doors [Delta]
channel.description:
In a delta-scape based source there is a door that is blocking my way it is in rimmington
Coords are between X:2964 Y:3206 [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/okpzj9.jpg[/img] And X:2965 Y:3206 [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/mbip9g.gif[/img]
I know how to remove models, just not doors.
P.S. No i can not just open the door

item.title: [Delta] How do you remove doors [Delta]
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

Make an object at the exact coords of the door, with id of -1.

Or if there’s a “remove object” packet, send that.
